    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and roughly chop your <strong>cooled egg[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>smoked basa fillet[s] </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
