    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>cornflour</strong>, <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>and <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[325ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
