    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the curried onions are fragrant, add the <strong>coconut stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce has thickened</p><p>Once thickened, add the <strong>chopped egg</strong>, <strong>chopped basa</strong>, <strong>blanched peas </strong>and<strong> spinach</strong> to the pan and stir everything together until fully combined</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min further or until the spinach has wilted – this is your <strong>curry fish pie mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
